**micrograd** A tiny Autograd engine. Implements backpropagation over a dynamically built DAG and a small
neural networks library on top of it with a Pytorch-like API.
-The notebook demo.ipynb provides a full demo of training an 2-layer neural network(MLP)binary classifier.
This is achieved by initializing a neural net from micrograd.nn module, implementing a simple svm "max-margin"binary
classification loss and using SGD for optimization.
